Description: OpenXR streaming application to a standalone headset
 WiVRn wirelessly connects a standalone VR headset to a Linu
 computer. You can then play PCVR games on the headset while
 processing is done on the computer.
 .
 It supports a wide range of headsets such as Quest 1 / 2 / Pro / 3,
 Pico Neo 3 / 4, HTC Vive Focus 3, HTC Vive XR elite and most
 other Android based headsets.
